11. Regex

AI can generate complex regex patterns in seconds.

Example Prompt:
â€œWrite a regex to validate a password with 8â€“16 chars, 1 uppercase, 1 number, and 1 special character.â€

12. Bash Scripts

Automate server operations.

Example Prompt:
â€œWrite a bash script to monitor CPU usage and alert if >80%.â€

13. Terraform Scripts

Automate infrastructure provisioning.

Example Prompt:
â€œWrite a Terraform script to deploy an AWS EC2 with security groups allowing SSH & HTTP.â€

14. CI/CD Configurations

Generate pipelines (GitLab, GitHub Actions, Jenkins).

Example Prompt:
â€œCreate a GitLab CI/CD pipeline for a Python Flask app with build, test, and deploy stages.â€
